#Paragraph: Youtube has always been an app I have been fond of as I have been watching videos and channels on it since the year it was released. 
#That's why I have decided to dive into this platform to uncover the secrets of what data builds up to getting a video on the trending page. 
#The dataset displayed statistics such as views, likes and comments that all adds up to determining which video gets displayed on the trending page.
#It is too vital of a role for how views and positive retention plays for a video to be trending. 
#With a surplus amount of online traction that are more than the channel's average retention, it could be the spark of having your video featured on trending.
